name: createDataStreamWithConfig
description:
Creates a data stream.Creates a data stream. Each user can create up to five data streams in a
                single channel.  
            Compared with createDataStream, this method does not
                support data reliability. If a data packet is not received five seconds after it was
                sent, the SDK directly discards the data.

parameters.config: The configurations for the data stream. See DataStreamConfig.

returns:
ID of the created data stream, if the method call succeeds.
       < 0: Failure. You can refer to Error Codes and Warning Codes for troubleshooting.
